{"tid":1078693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴力男偷飛機 低空衝刺撞妻！夫陷火海亡","createTime":"2019-03-26T12:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T13:46:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cb85f730cd31da4489712d96316738e67576e5f6","tid":1078693,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:26:55.000Z","msg":"有需要氣到賭上性命嗎？非洲波札那（Botswana）一名機師維爾亞恩（Charl Viljoen）和妻子娜塔莎（Natasha Viljoen）在一場派對中發生爭吵，2人隨後被其他賓客趕出會場，怎料，機師一氣之下，直接偷開附近的小型飛機，以低水平「死亡衝刺」的方式將俱樂部撞毀，機師當場身亡，所幸賓客和妻子在事發前早已逃離會場，無人傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，當地時間23日晚間，機師和妻子正在參加一場生產前的慶祝派對（BABY SHOWER），沒想到夫妻倆卻突然在會場起了爭執，甚至大打出手，有目擊者表示，「實際上他（機師）打了他妻子，於是每個人都請他滾出去，因為沒有人會這樣對待女人」。<br />\n<br />\n原以為整起事件就此落幕，令人意想不到的是，機師離開後，竟直接偷走一架小型飛機King Air 200，期間，他還致電向朋友詢問「妻子是否還在那」，接著就以低水平飛越會場上空，準備朝飛行俱樂部俯衝，幸好當時飛機經過塔台的時候，俱樂部內的民眾發覺事態不對勁，便緊急呼叫賓客們逃到外面躲避攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n畫面中可以看見，肇事機師駕駛的飛機幾乎以貼地的高度，快速衝向會場，形同「毀滅式的飛行方式」，撞上俱樂部後，飛機當場爆炸，附近13輛汽車全遭燒毀，機師瞬間陷入火海當場身亡，幸好最後無其他人員傷亡。對此，俱樂部也表示，該名機師根本「無權駕駛飛機」。消息曝光後，許多人都對這名機師的行徑感到不可置信，紛紛留言：「他為什麼不能等她回家後再處理」、「為什麼要用這麼昂貴的方式自殺」、「如果想要輕生，也不該駕駛飛機衝向還在舉辦派對的俱樂部，這樣很自私」、「這已經不是輕生，而是恐怖份子」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2019/03/26/1553594525_80030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2019%2F03%2F26%2F1553594525_80030.jpg&h=69d5289a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2019/03/26/1553593577_84981.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2019%2F03%2F26%2F1553593577_84981.jpg&h=999de8fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2019/03/26/1553593773_36438.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2019%2F03%2F26%2F1553593773_36438.JPG&h=20d4d401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2019/03/26/1553593791_49565.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2019%2F03%2F26%2F1553593791_49565.JPG&h=f5f92e30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e863f555063f92a5e7acb3e712eb2f4a49915be","tid":1078693,"uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n霸氣！男人典範！<br />\n<br />\n一定要入男人教科書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77ad009986e5eed34a22e833a542de46fec37d4","tid":1078693,"uid":30006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"玩開Battlefield ？"},{"pid":"e7f8c90b189abb7124670493977c91a646f55421","tid":1078693,"uid":26168,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"咁似達哥會做嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1262fb50bd1fa330ac994a59a2605f7b759cf2","tid":1078693,"uid":33206,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"0 kill, 1 death, score -10"},{"pid":"8000f922fa716e97a8b7eb3e12c457e07b9af0cf","tid":1078693,"uid":119007,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:38:28.000Z","msg":"所幸賓客和妻子在事發前早已逃離會場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408b805947f2b5b6680ebe77a5b9d2db15e41889","tid":1078693,"uid":51724,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e7f8c90b189abb7124670493977c91a646f55421","tid":1078693,"uid":26168,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"咁似達哥會做嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"達哥: 諗到個新玩法"},{"pid":"d9ea059028953f9117f7dacc3115ede9b603335f","tid":1078693,"uid":26168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"408b805947f2b5b6680ebe77a5b9d2db15e41889","tid":1078693,"u